Some Calibre recipes for (mostly) Hungarian websites (and blogs).

The recipes can be run via the Calibre GUI, or via the installed Calibre tools, e.g.:

    ebook-convert \
        SOME.recipe \
        OUTPUTFILE.EBOOKFORMAT \
        --output-profile kindle 
        -vv 
        --pretty-print 
        --change-justification justify 
        -d dbdir

In the above case, the e-book-format should be mobi, as it's the desired format for the selected profile (kindle). The lines below the OUTPUTFILE.EBOOKFORMAT are not necessary.
